      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey everyone!<br />\nWe’re excited to share that <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000472/calendar-masterplan\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MasterPlan Calendar</a> is now fully compatible with the <a href=\"https://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> mobile app ,making it one of the first marketplace apps with true mobile functionality <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/iphone.png?v=15\" title=\":iphone:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":iphone:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=15\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> .</p>\n<p>You can now:<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Display your calendar in <strong>day, week, month, or list</strong> views<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Create new item events</strong> directly from mobile<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Update existing events</strong> on the go</p>\n<p>If you’ve been looking for a way to manage your <a href=\"https://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> schedule while away from your desk, this is now possible!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=683a850898635b63ab88424554eecdec&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Install MasterPlan Calendar on your account</a></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/1/b124c56d3c74d864ef7acb02fa82498bd5f74589.jpeg\" title=\"Frame 97\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/1/b124c56d3c74d864ef7acb02fa82498bd5f74589_2_690x414.jpeg\" alt=\"Frame 97\" width=\"690\" height=\"414\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Frame 97</span><span class=\"informations\">3200×1920 450 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
